    public class DataObjectFactory.DataObjectIntegerInput
extends IntegerInput
implements DataObjectItemInput<BDO>
    A basic form Input for selecting objects using their ID value as text. Only use this where the table is too large to support a pull-down. To make text forms easier to use the input will attempt to look up the target by name if the parent factory implements NameFinder.
